OL,3,CHuman rights law overhaul planned as
OL,4,Cpart of UK's asylum reforms
OL,6,FShabana Mahmood has announced a
OL,7,Fsweeping reform of the UK's asylum
OL,8,Fsystem - and said that illegal
OL,9,Fmigration is 'tearing the country
OL,10,Fapart', as ITV News Political
OL,11,FCorrespondent Shehab Khan reports
OL,13,FMinisters will overhaul human rights
OL,14,Flaws to make it easier to deport
OL,15,Fillegal migrants, as part of a major
OL,16,Fshake-up of the asylum system.
