OL,3,CHuman rights law overhaul planned as
OL,4,Cpart of UK's asylum reforms
OL,6,FBilled as the largest change to the
OL,7,FUK's system in the modern era, Home
OL,8,FSecretary Shabana Mahmood plans to
OL,9,Frewrite how Britain grants refuge to
OL,10,Fthose fleeing conflict and upheaval
OL,11,Fwith a statement in the House of
OL,12,FCommons on Monday.
OL,14,FShe will bring forward a Bill to
OL,15,Fchange how article 8 of the European
OL,16,FConvention on Human Rights (ECHR), the
OL,17,Fright to family life, is applied in
OL,18,Fmigration court cases.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
