OL,3,CHuman rights law overhaul planned as
OL,4,Cpart of UK's asylum reforms
OL,6,FThe home secretary also plans to
OL,7,Fchange the law so that multiple
OL,8,Fattempts to appeal against refusals
OL,9,Ffor asylum will no longer be allowed.
OL,11,FJudges will be asked to balance that
OL,12,Fright against the wider public
OL,13,Finterest under the reforms.
OL,15,FMahmood insisted that the overhaul was
OL,16,Fneeded because the current system is
OL,17,F"out of control" and is causing "huge
OL,18,Fdivision" across the country.
