OL,3,CHuman rights law overhaul planned as
OL,4,Cpart of UK's asylum reforms
OL,6,FOn Sunday, the home secretary warned
OL,7,Fthat public consent for the asylum
OL,8,Fsystem may disappear if her major
OL,9,Freforms are not introduced.
OL,11,FShe also said: "I have no doubt about
OL,12,Fwho we really are in this country. We
OL,13,Fare open, tolerant and generous.
OL,15,F"But I also know there are conditions
OL,16,Fto that.
OL,18,F"The public rightly expects that we
OL,19,Fcan determine who enters this country,
OL,20,Fand who must leave.
