OL,6,F"To maintain the generosity that
OL,7,Fallows us to provide sanctuary, we
OL,8,Fmust restore order and control."
OL,10,FCharities have branded the home
OL,11,Fsecretary's plans "harsh and
OL,12,Funnecessary", and said they "won't
OL,13,Fdeter people who have been persecuted,
OL,14,Ftortured or seen family members killed
OL,15,Fin brutal wars".
