OL,3,CHuman rights law overhaul planned as
OL,4,Cpart of UK's asylum reforms
OL,6,FThe Home Office said it had seen a
OL,7,Frise in the use of rights-based
OL,8,Fappeals in recent years as a means of
OL,9,Favoiding deportation, including by
OL,10,Fserious criminals intent on staying in
OL,11,FBritain.
OL,13,FOnly those with immediate family in
OL,14,Fthe UK, such as a parent or child,
OL,15,Fwill be able to use Article 8 as
OL,16,Fgrounds to stay in future.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
