OL,3,CHuman rights law overhaul planned as
OL,4,Cpart of UK's asylum reforms
OL,6,FMahmood is also expected to restrict
OL,7,Ffailed asylum seekers to a single
OL,8,Froute of appeal, preventing them from
OL,9,Fmaking multiple attempts to stay in
OL,10,Fthe UK and delaying their removal.
OL,12,FA new independent body ` similar to
OL,13,Fone in operation in Denmark ` will be
OL,14,Fset up to fast-track the removal of
OL,15,Fdangerous criminals, and last-minute
OL,16,Fappeals will be expedited.
OL,18,FSimilarly, claims by migrants that
OL,19,Fthey are facing modern slavery will be
OL,20,Fmore closely scrutinised as a result
OL,21,Fof tweaks to the Modern Slavery Act.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
