OL,6,F"But in a more volatile world, people
OL,7,Fneed to know our borders are secure
OL,8,Fand rules are enforced. These reforms
OL,9,Fwill block endless appeals, stop last-
OL,10,Fminute claims and scale up removals of
OL,11,Fthose with no right to be here."
OL,13,FWhat proposals have been announced?
OL,15,FOther reforms already trailed as part
OL,16,Fof the raft of reforms include that
OL,17,Frefugee status will be made temporary
OL,18,Fand subject to regular review under
OL,19,Fthe proposals, so that people are
OL,20,Freturned to their homeland once it
OL,21,Fbecomes safe.
