OL,6,FMinisters have taken inspiration from
OL,7,Fthe strict asylum approach taken by
OL,8,FDenmark, where a government of the
OL,9,Fsame political stripe as Labour has
OL,10,Fmanaged to remove incentives drawing
OL,11,Fpeople to the country and has
OL,12,Fincreased deportations of illegal
OL,13,Fmigrants.
OL,15,FSome 39,075 people have arrived in the
OL,16,FUK after making the journey so far
OL,17,Fthis year, according to the latest
OL,18,FHome Office figures.
