OL,12,Fadvocating on behalf of refugees,
OL,13,Fwarned that the government's plans
OL,14,Fwould accrue a cost of #872 million
OL,15,Fover ten years as a result of the need
OL,16,Fto review asylum seekers' status to
OL,17,Fremain in the UK.
