OL,6,FEnver Solomon, the charity's chief
OL,7,Fexecutive, insisted the changes "will
OL,8,Fnot deter people from making dangerous
OL,9,Fcrossings, but they will unfairly
OL,10,Fprevent men, women and children from
OL,11,Fintegrating into British life".
OL,13,FHe added: "This isn't who we are as a
OL,14,Fnation, and it has echoes of how
OL,15,Fhardworking people who came to our
OL,16,Fcountry as migrants were so badly
OL,17,Ftreated by the Windrush scandal."
